sentence: Wednesday's session closes with the NASDAQ Composite Index reaching a historical high.
The index closed at 5,656.34 up 55.38 for the day.
The index first reached the 5000 mark on 01/24/2017 The total shares traded for the NASDAQ was over 2.06 billion.
Advancers stocks led declining by 2.37 to 1 ratio.
There were 2022 advancers and 853 decliners for the day.
On the NASDAQ Stock Exchange 212 stocks reached a 52 week high and 14 reaching lows.
The most active, advancers, decliners, unusual volume and most active by dollar volume can be monitored intraday on the Most Active Stocks page.
The NASDAQ 100 index closed up .99% for the day; a total of 50.41 points.
CA Inc. ( CA ) had the largest percent change down (-4.98%) while Seagate Technology PLC ( STX ) had the largest percent change gain rising 13.97%.
The Dow Jones index closed up .78% for the day; a total of 155.8 points.
Procter & Gamble Company (The) ( PG ) had the largest percent change down (-.8%) while Boeing Company (The) ( BA ) had the largest percent change gain rising 4.24%.
